---
import Card from "./Card/index.astro";
---

<Card colSpan="md:col-span-1" rowSpan="md:row-span-6" title="About me">
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
    <div class="text-sm font-light">
      <p>
        I'm Ayush, an M.Tech CSE student at IIT Patna focused on secure
        software engineering.
        <br />
        I usually work with:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
        <li>Python, C, and C++</li>
        <li>FastAPI and Redis</li>
        <li>Web app testing with Burp Suite</li>
        <li>OWASP Top 10 and VAPT workflows</li>
        <li>Networking, OS, DBMS, and system design basics</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <p class="text-sm font-light">
      My recent projects include secure asynchronous task processing and
      authentication-flow analysis for real systems.
    </p>
    <p class="text-sm font-light">
      I care about building products that stay usable under pressure: clean
      architecture, careful threat modeling, and fixes developers can actually
      implement.
    </p>
  </div>
</Card>
